## folder structure  q use karte hain?

a) Separation of Concerns (SoC)

index.js → Server aur app ka entry point
routes/ → URL endpoints define karte hain
controllers/ → Route logic ko handle karte hain
models/ → Database schema aur data structure
config/ → Configuration like DB connection
middleware/ → Authentication, logging, error handling
utils/ → Helper functions


✅ Fayda:
Readable & Maintainable: Bada project bhi easily samajh aata hai
Scalable: Naye features add karna simple
Team-friendly: Multiple developers easily kaam kar sakte hain



b) Modularity

Agar aapko sirf user module ko alag server me move karna ho → easy
Ya fir naye route add karna ho → sirf routes/ aur controllers/ me changes

